                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><date>Decbr. 7<hi rend=\"sup\">Th</hi> 1862</date>.</p>\n            <p><addressee>Revd Is. Leeser</addressee>,</p>\n            <p>Sir.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I received the Occident<lb/> yesterday—which was the first<lb/>\n                intimation I had from you that<lb/> you had received my letter.<lb/> I supposed a\n                letter from a<lb/> lady was worthy a reply.<lb/> I do not know on what terms<lb/>\n                you have inserted the adver-<lb/>tisement; it is of no importance<lb/> and, as I\n                wish to discontinue<lb/> advertising in your columns—as in<lb/> the <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">insulting</hi> manner, you have<lb/> published the same, you\n                would render<lb/> me more injury than service:<lb/> you are the same Sir, as\n                the<lb/> rest of the world—a <hi rend=\"underline\">friend</hi> in<lb/> prosperity but\n                ready to add a pang<lb/> to the mind of a man in adversity</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p35q4s63z/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
